Revision history for Perl extension XML::Generator::DBI.

1.00
    - Ported to SAX2 API
    - Added GroupBy support, which implements group functionality based
      on a changing column value
    - Added ByColumnName support, which allows you to create arbitrary
      XML structures using "col as 'a/b/c'" aliases (see docs for more details).
    - Major refactoring

0.03
    - Fixed bug where if Indent was on, newline got
      sent after the last close tag, which is invalid in XML

0.02
    - Converted to use XML::SAX::Base
    - Performance tweaks
    - Indent is off by default
    
0.01  Thu Aug  2 17:47:34 2001
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.19

